Slider:
------

--->dragandDropBy(Element,x,y)

first we need to get the position of the web element by using getPosition() it return (x,y)

for horizontal we need to increase or decrease the x value
for Vertical we need to increase or decrease the y value

KeyboardActions:
----------------
1.KeyDown(Keys.CTRL) - press down the ctrl key
2.KeyUp(Keys.CTRL)- release the ctrl key
3.Sendkeys("A") - send the alphabets

example:
-------
ctrl+A-- 2 keys
KeyDown(Keys.CTRL).sendkeys("A").KeyUp(Keys.CTRL).perform()

Ctrl+Shift+A -- 3 keys
KeyDown(Keys.CTRL).KeyDown(Keys.SHIFT).sendkeys("A").KeyUp(Keys.SHIFT).KeyUp(Keys.CTRL).perform()

